                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colspan="4" spanname="SPAN2">
                                <para>Comments</para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colspan="4" spanname="SPAN2" align="center">
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">Relay to Harness Connector</emph>- High resistance could indicate
                                    an open circuit in the engine harness between the glow plug connector and the relay.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colspan="4" spanname="SPAN2" align="center">
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">Breakout Connector to Ground</emph>- High resistance could
                                    indicate an open circuit in the UVC (Under Valve Cover) harness or in the glow plug.
                                    Glow plug resistance should measure less than 6 ohms dependent upon engine
                                    temperature.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colspan="4" spanname="SPAN2" align="center">
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">DTC (DIAGNOSTIC TROUBLE CODES)</emph>
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colspan="4" spanname="SPAN2" align="center">
                                <para>251 = OCC CHK performed by ECM during engine off test. Indicates high or low
                                    resistance in GP coil circuit.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry colspan="4" spanname="SPAN2" align="center">
                                <para>252 = OCC CHK performed by ECM during engine off test. Indicates high or low
                                    resistance in GP lamp circuit.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
