            <specpara>
                <note>
                    <para>The injector circuits are not available on the breakout box due to high voltage. The testing
                        of these circuits must be made by removing the connector from the ECM and testing directly at
                        the terminals.
                    </para>
                </note>
            </specpara>
            <figure id="p014906" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../tsifigures/F0901.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
